file.name: schema.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: userapi
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://localhost:8080
    description: development
paths:
  /users:
    get:
      description: Userをすべて取得する
      operationId: getUsers
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Users'
components:
  schemas:
    Users:
      type: object
      properties:
        users:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/UserProperties'
      required:
        - users
    UserProperties:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          example: 1
        name:
          type: string
          example: po3rin
      required:
        - id
        - name

  responses:
    Users:
      description: Userの配列
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Users'
